entry.def: If something can be easily recognized or identified, you can say that it is easily recognizable .

example.ex: The body was found to be well preserved, his features easily recognizable...
example.tran: 尸体保存完好，他的容貌特征清晰可辨。

example.ex: This tree is always recognizable by its extremely beautiful silvery bark.
example.tran: 这种树很容易辨认，因为它有着非常漂亮的银色树皮。
